- Framework for creatign serverless apps in aws
- docs.amplify.aws

Steps: Create backend app or host webapp
------
1) npm install -g @aws-amplify/cli
2) amplify configure
3) Select region and user to work with amplify
4) Create a skeleton app
5) amplify init  //A project will be created cloud
6) amplify add auth
7) amplify push
8) npm add aws-amplify @aws-amplify/ui-vue
9) Amplify publish



amplify add api
amplify push